Package pegasus.container

Interface DoubleContainer

All Superinterfaces:
BaseContainer<Double>, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DoubleArrayElementReference, DoubleVariableReference, FastDoubleContainer
public interface DoubleContainer extends BaseContainer<Double>
A value-based primitive container of a double value.
